&gt;  Hello All! I just recently discovered this group through the
&gt;  Ufogeek&#39;s website. I have been experiencing shadows, electrical
&gt;  sensations that feel like someone else is with me. With that being
&gt;  said, I ask if this technology you all talk about on this group would
&gt;  help me speak with those presences I feel with me?

Yes.  I have some mediumistic abilities and find working with my Shack 
hack as a good complement to that.  I&#39;ve gotten confirmation through the 
box of some things I&#39;d been told psychically.  It&#39;s also been helpful in 
that getting information in a physical/auditory manner helps keep me 
from thinking that the psychic stuff is all just my imagination.

&gt;  I was
&gt;  hoping this technology would help me understand the presences that
&gt;  come to me.

I&#39;ll second the suggestion to go into it with a positive frame of mind.  
Other than that, I can truthfully say that it&#39;s helped me in that respect.


Nellie


